        <ul>
            <li>Compute &epsilon;-closure of NFA's start state.</li>
            <li>For each state set and input symbol, compute transitions.</li>
            <li>Add new state sets to DFA.</li>
            <li>Mark final states containing NFA's final states.</li>
        </ul>
